(blinking of light).

Hardware Requirement.

-Rasberry pi kit
-Monitor
-key board
-Mouse.

Software Requirement:

→Rasberry os
→Thonny

Circuit diagram:



import RPi. GPIO as GPIO
import time
GPIO. Setwarnings (False)
GPIO setmode (GPIO BCM)
GPIP. Setup (4, GPIO Out)
While true:
GPIO. Output (4 , GPIO .HIGH)
time. sleep (1)
GPIO. Output (4, GPIO.LOW)
time. sleep (1)
